description:
Adrianna Nicole a.k.a. "The Adrianaconda" 2-0, ranked 7th. Currently undefeated, and on a roll. She is big, strong and has the determination to win. Adrianna uses her size and strength to easily overcome her opponents.
Wenona a.k.a. "The Gymnast" 5-5, ranked 5th. Wenona is undefeated this season, and has the experience of 10 matches to draw from. Wenona has amazingly strong killer legs and has gotten over 13 submissions to date.
Wenona has the experience advantage, however she is giving up over 20lbs to the new upstart Adrianna Nicole. Will Wenona's amazing enduranc and strong legs overcome the determination and brute power of the "The Adrianaconda?" Which girls gets brutally fucked by the winner after the match? Only one way to find out who wins this non-scripted real event.
title: Adrianna Nicole "The Adrianaconda" (2-0)
